рџ“Џ LГЌMITES DE CГ“DIGO
в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ

| Tipo       | LГ­mite | AcciГіn                        |
|------------|--------|-------------------------------|
| Widget     | 300    | Extraer subwidgets            |
| Servicio   | 400    | Dividir responsabilidades     |
| Provider   | 300    | Crear sub-providers           |
| Modelo     | 150    | Usar composition              |
| FunciГіn    | 50     | Extraer helpers               |
| ParГЎmetros | 5      | Usar objetos de configuraciГіn |

в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
 TESTING
в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ

-  Widgets crГ­ticos deben tener tests
-  Providers/Services:  unit tests cuando sea viable
-  No usar Firebase real en tests (usar mocks)
-  `flutter analyze` debe pasar sin errores
-  `flutter test` debe pasar todos los tests

## Estructura de Tests
```dart
// test/services/my_service_test.dart
void main() {
  group('MyService', () {
    late MyService service;
    
    setUp(() {
      service = MyService();
    });
    
    test('should return valid data', () async {
      final result = await service.getData();
      expect(result, isNotNull);
    });
  });
}
```

